OL,3,CMan with chronic neurological
OL,4,Ccondition brands benefits overhaul
OL,5,C'offensive'
OL,7,FDavid Colley, who has a chronic
OL,8,Fneurological condition, says he is
OL,9,Fterrified about what an overhaul to
OL,10,Fthe benefit system could mean for him
OL,11,Ffinancially
OL,13,FA North Tyneside man who cannot work
OL,14,Fdue to a chronic neurological
OL,15,Fcondition has branded changes to the
OL,16,Fbenefit system announced by the
OL,17,Fgovernment as "offensive".
