OL,3,CMan with chronic neurological
OL,4,Ccondition brands benefits overhaul
OL,5,C'offensive'
OL,7,FThe changes include tightening the
OL,8,Feligibility criteria for disability
OL,9,Fbenefits, scrapping a controversial
OL,10,Fbenefits assessment, and raising the
OL,11,Fbasic rate of universal credit while
OL,12,Fcutting the higher rate for those too
OL,13,Fill to work.
OL,15,FBut Mr Colley, a wheelchair user,
OL,16,Fbelieves disabled people are being
OL,17,Fused as an "easy target" and says the
OL,18,Fchanges are "offensive".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
