OL,7,FMr Colley is a Labour Party member and
OL,8,Fhas told us he is so offended by what
OL,9,Fhas been announced that he intends to
OL,10,Fgive up his membership.
OL,12,FSpeaking in the Commons, Ms Kendall
OL,13,Fannounced the eligibility criteria for
OL,14,FPIP will be tightened, with people
OL,15,Fhaving to prove more severe
OL,16,Fdifficulties in order to qualify.
