OL,7,FIt is a benefit designed to help
OL,8,Fpeople with a disability to pay for
OL,9,Fadditional costs, such as wheelchairs,
OL,10,Fcars, above average bills, carers, and
OL,11,Fspecialist equipment.
OL,13,FMr Colley has said he relies on PIP to
OL,14,Fmake ends meet, and is very concerned
OL,15,Fabout the possibility of losing it.
