OL,7,FHe said: "It's terrifying, because it
OL,8,Fcomes amongst a lot of other financial
OL,9,Fproblems as a disabled person. We
OL,10,Fcan't afford our bills, with the price
OL,11,Fof fuel at the moment, for winter for
OL,12,Fme I could only afford to have my
OL,13,Fheating on one hour a day.
OL,15,F"When I've got to reapply now for my
OL,16,FPIP, am I going to get it? Will I have
OL,17,Fthe evidence? Who have I got to go to
OL,18,Fto get the evidence? What have I got
OL,19,Fto prove?"
