OL,7,FThe Prime Minister said the measures
OL,8,Fwere needed to address a system which
OL,9,F"does not work for the people it is
OL,10,Fsupposed to support, businesses who
OL,11,Fneed workers or taxpayers who foot the
OL,12,Fbill".
OL,14,FSir Keir Starmer said: "This
OL,15,FGovernment will always protect the
OL,16,Fmost severely disabled people to live
OL,17,Fwith dignity.
